  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-eyebrow">About</div>
    <h1>Longevity intelligence<br><em>for everyone.</em></h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <div class="lead">
      Most people receive their blood test results as a list of numbers with no context. AgelessLabs exists to change that — giving anyone access to the kind of deep biomarker interpretation that was previously only available to patients of expensive longevity clinics.
    </div>

    <div class="content-block">
      <h2>The problem we're solving</h2>
      <p>Standard reference ranges on blood tests are designed to detect disease — not to optimize for longevity. A result marked "normal" by your doctor may still be far from the range associated with a long, healthy life. Most people have no way of knowing the difference.</p>
      <p>At the same time, the science of longevity has advanced rapidly. We now know which biomarkers matter most for healthspan, what optimal ranges look like, and what interventions actually move the needle. That knowledge exists — but it's locked inside specialist clinics, academic papers, and expensive concierge medicine programs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="content-block">
      <h2>What AgelessLabs does</h2>
      <p>AgelessLabs is an AI-powered platform that interprets your blood test results through a longevity lens. Upload your labs — as a PDF, an image, or pasted text — and our AI analyzes every marker against longevity-optimized ranges, generates a personalized score, and tells you exactly what to do next.</p>
      <p>It's not a replacement for your doctor. It's the context your doctor doesn't have time to give you — and the second opinion you've always wanted.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="content-block">
      <h2>Our principles</h2>
      <div class="values">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-label">Accuracy first</div>
          <div class="value-text">We interpret biomarkers based on the best available longevity science — not commercial incentives or outdated reference ranges.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-label">Radical transparency</div>
          <div class="value-text">We explain every recommendation. You should always know why a marker matters and what the evidence says.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-label">Privacy by design</div>
          <div class="value-text">Your health data is yours. We don't store your lab results and never will.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-label">Accessible longevity</div>
          <div class="value-text">The science of living longer shouldn't be a luxury. Our core tool is free and always will be.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="content-block">
      <h2>Who built this</h2>
      <p>AgelessLabs was built by <strong>Dan Carey</strong>, an ecommerce entrepreneur with 25 years of experience building digital products, and a longtime personal advocate for proactive health optimization.</p>
      <p>Like most people, I spent years getting blood tests back with no real context — just a list of numbers and a "looks normal" from my doctor. AgelessLabs exists because that's not good enough.</p>
